ton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2527486\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2527486\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104fgk1665702598390.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fgk1665702598390.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fgk1665702598390.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"fgk1665702598390\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $hits\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"fgk1665702598390___hits_267939\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the number of occurrences in the hitlist.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"fgk1665702598390__topic_d84257e1_d84258e1_d84259e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fgk1665702598390__p_d84260e1_d84261e1_d84262e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$hits</span> { <code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code> }</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fgk1665702598390__topic_d55797e1_d55798e1_d55799e1_d55800e1_d55801e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d544335e75\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"fgk1665702598390__d6092e20\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fgk1665702598390__d6092e20__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fgk1665702598390__d6092e20__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fgk1665702598390__d6092e20__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fgk1665702598390__d6092e20__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fgk1665702598390__d6092e20__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fgk1665702598390__d6092e20__entry__3\">\n Entity name; optional. If omitted, the current entity is used.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fgk1665702598390__topic_d55802e1_d55803e1_d55804e1_d55805e1_d55806e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d544335e129\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fgk1665702598390__li_d34403e1_d34404e1_d34405e1\">Total number of occurrences in the hitlist.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fgk1665702598390__li_d34406e1_d34407e1_d34408e1\">An empty string (\"\") if an error occurred. <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> contains a negative value that identifies the exact error.\n </li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"fgk1665702598390__table_d8738e1_d8739e1_d8740e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> Commonly Returned Following\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$hits</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fgk1665702598390__table_d8738e1_d8739e1_d8740e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Value \n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fgk1665702598390__table_d8738e1_d8739e1_d8740e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Error constant\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fgk1665702598390__table_d8738e1_d8739e1_d8740e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fgk1665702598390__table_d8738e1_d8739e1_d8740e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fgk1665702598390__table_d8738e1_d8739e1_d8740e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n &lt;UIOSERR_*&gt; (-2 through -12)\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fgk1665702598390__table_d8738e1_d8739e1_d8740e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Errors during database I/O.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fgk1665702598390__table_d8738e1_d8739e1_d8740e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fgk1665702598390__table_d8738e1_d8739e1_d8740e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n &lt;UNETERR_*&gt; (-16 through -30)\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fgk1665702598390__table_d8738e1_d8739e1_d8740e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Errors during network I/O.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fgk1665702598390__table_d8738e1_d8739e1_d8740e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n -1102\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fgk1665702598390__table_d8738e1_d8739e1_d8740e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n &lt;UPROCERR_ENTITY&gt;\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fgk1665702598390__table_d8738e1_d8739e1_d8740e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n The entity name provided is not a valid name or the entity is not painted on the component.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fgk1665702598390__topic_d55807e1_d55808e1_d55809e1_d55810e1_d55811e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d544335e220\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fgk1665702598390__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fgk1665702598390__topic_d55812e1_d55813e1_d55814e1_d55815e1_d55816e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d544335e230\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fgk1665702598390__p_d84278e1_d84279e1_d84280e1\">If the DBMS you are accessing supports a stepped hitlist, any performance benefits derived from use of the stepped hitlist are lost when you use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$hits</span>, since building the complete hitlist can be quite time-consuming.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"fgk1665702598390__table_d8741e1_d8742e1_d8743e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 3. </span><span class=\"title\">Statements that Change<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$hits</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fgk1665702598390__table_d8741e1_d8742e1_d8743e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Event\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fgk1665702598390__table_d8741e1_d8742e1_d8743e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Action\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fgk1665702598390__table_d8741e1_d8742e1_d8743e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rig1719386303130.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rig1719386303130.html\" title=\"Clear data from the component or entity.\">clear</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fgk1665702598390__table_d8741e1_d8742e1_d8743e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">Sets <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$hits</span> to\n                           <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fgk1665702598390__table_d8741e1_d8742e1_d8743e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vxw1719821718668.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vxw1719821718668.html\" title=\"Release database controls.\">release</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fgk1665702598390__table_d8741e1_d8742e1_d8743e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">Sets <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$hits</span> to\n                           <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fgk1665702598390__table_d8741e1_d8742e1_d8743e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lsx1665702598541.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lsx1665702598541.html\" title=\"Remove one or more occurrences from the component and the hitlist.\">discard</a>\n<p class=\"p\">\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fgk1665702598390__table_d8741e1_d8742e1_d8743e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Reduces <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$hits</span> by the number of discarded occurrences.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"fgk1665702598390__note_w179ab1b7c11b7_w180ab1b7c11_w181ab1b7_w182ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> The Debugger does not build the complete hitlist if you examine\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$hits</span>. Instead, it returns the value in\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$curhits</span>.</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fgk1665702598390__section_rqk_2d1_1cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d544335e349\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$hits</span></h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following example shows the exec operation of a form. This\n               ProcScript copies a value into the form which defines a profile, then retrieves all\n               the companies which match that profile. The assignment statement copies the total\n               number of hits which match the profile to a dummy field in the footer frame on the\n               form:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"fgk1665702598390__pre_fg5_2d1_1cc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation exec\n COMPNAME = $1\n retrieve\n if ($status &lt; 0)\n message \"Retrieve error\"\n exit (0)\n endif\n TOTSEL.TRAILER = $hits(COMPANY)\n display COMPNAME\nend; exec</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ebm1665702598309.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>lookup</a><p>Count the number of occurrences that match the current profile.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cyd1665702599286.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>retrieve</a><p>Activate the read trigger for the first outermost entity and all related entities, or for a specific entity.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vhw1665702560221.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>setocc</a><p>Make a specific occurrence the current occurrence.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xmg1665702599090.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$curhits</a><p>Return the number of occurrences in the hitlist.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fio1665702598862.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$dbocc</a><p>Return the sequence number of the current occurrence within the set of occurrences retrieved from the database.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527486\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527486\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$hits Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $hits Return the number of occurrences in the hitlist. $hits { ( Entity ) } Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description Entity String Entity name; optional. If omitted, the current entity is used. Return Values Total number of occurrences in the hitlist. An empty string (\"\") if an error occurred. $procerror contains a negative value that identifies the exact error. Table 2. Values of $procerror Commonly Returned Following $hits Value Error constant Meaning <UIOSERR_*> (-2 through -12) Errors during database I/O. <UNETERR_*> (-16 through -30) Errors during network I/O. -1102 <UPROCERR_ENTITY> The entity name provided is not a valid name or the entity is not painted on the component. Use Allowed in all component types. Description If the DBMS you are accessing supports a stepped hitlist, any performance benefits derived from use of the stepped hitlist are lost when you use $hits , since building the complete hitlist can be quite time-consuming. Table 3. Statements that Change $hits Event Action clear Sets $hits to 0 . release Sets $hits to 0 . discard Reduces $hits by the number of discarded occurrences. Note: The Debugger does not build the complete hitlist if you examine $hits . Instead, it returns the value in $curhits . Example: Using $hits The following example shows the exec operation of a form. This ProcScript copies a value into the form which defines a profile, then retrieves all the companies which match that profile. The assignment statement copies the total number of hits which match the profile to a dummy field in the footer frame on the form: operation exec COMPNAME = $1 retrieve if ($status < 0) message \"Retrieve error\" exit (0) endif TOTSEL.TRAILER = $hits(COMPANY) display COMPNAME end; exec Copy Related Links lookup Count the number of occurrences that match the current profile. retrieve Activate the read trigger for the first outermost entity and all related entities, or for a specific entity. setocc Make a specific occurrence the current occurrence. $curhits Return the number of occurrences in the hitlist. $dbocc Return the sequence number of the current occurrence within the set of occurrences retrieved from the database. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}